node.text: Before we wrap up one of the wildest years, we’re taking a look back at our favorite @stockxteam highlights. Through it all, the crew shattered records, launched campaigns, supported important causes, partnered with insanely talented collaborators, AND hit $2.8 billy - all thanks to YOU. 2021, we’re ready for ya 😤

node.text: Two specially-crafted decks and t-shirts from @berrics and @everybodyskates are now available exclusively on StockX. Designed by legendary pro @alphonzorawls, this limited ‘Thank You’ collection pays homage to the diversity within skateboarding, featuring the names of influential Black and Brown skateboarders from the last 40 years. Limited quantities are up for grabs, so tap fast to secure yours. A portion of proceeds will support the @nextupfound.
